1
00:01:57,110 --> 00:02:01,990
=Yummy Yummy Yummy=

2
00:02:02,780 --> 00:02:04,940
=Episode 2=

3
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:09,680
Be careful!

4
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:12,740
(Yunshui Manor)

5
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:26,400
Vice Prefect Lin, sorry.

6
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:28,150
Sir, sorry.

7
00:02:28,350 --> 00:02:29,280
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

8
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,120
Get up.

9
00:02:37,150 --> 00:02:38,030
Who are you?

10
00:02:38,740 --> 00:02:39,860
Greetings, Vice Prefect Lin.

11
00:02:40,220 --> 00:02:41,420
I am Shen Shaoguang.

12
00:02:41,420 --> 00:02:43,000
My family has a stall in Juxian Alley.

13
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,300
I heard that you've taken office.

14
00:02:44,300 --> 00:02:46,200
Your food on the way
might not be good enough,

15
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:48,000
so I came to make
Jianbing Guozi for you,

16
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,140
delivering pancakes to you.

17
00:02:49,140 --> 00:02:51,100
It's straight
to the Vice Prefect's face.

18
00:02:51,740 --> 00:02:53,060
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

19
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:55,500
You are

20
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:57,700
Shen Shaoguang?

21
00:02:58,860 --> 00:03:00,140
I'll give you another chance.

22
00:03:00,580 --> 00:03:01,560
Reveal the ringleader,

23
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,940
restore the normal market price,

24
00:03:02,940 --> 00:03:03,860
and never do it again.

25
00:03:04,260 --> 00:03:05,260
Reveal the mastermind.

26
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:06,460
Mastermind?

27
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:08,380
I know. It's my sister Shen Shaoguang.

28
00:03:08,380 --> 00:03:09,460
It was all her idea.

29
00:03:09,460 --> 00:03:10,580
She said to have an auction,

30
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:11,700
and then we'd make a fortune.

31
00:03:16,140 --> 00:03:17,460
Vice Prefect, you know me?

32
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:20,140
I've become so famous so quickly?

33
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:22,060
The Pancake Belle?

34
00:03:23,020 --> 00:03:23,860
Alright.

35
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:25,020
Go back now.

36
00:03:25,420 --> 00:03:27,020
Don't inflate the prices ever again.

37
00:03:27,420 --> 00:03:28,780
Otherwise, you'll be flogged.

38
00:03:29,260 --> 00:03:30,580
What do you mean?

39
00:03:31,260 --> 00:03:32,260
Don't you know

40
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:34,300
what you've done?

41
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:37,900
(Yunshui Manor)
Vice Prefect Lin, I...

42
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:38,900
Stop!

43
00:03:39,420 --> 00:03:40,260
Auntie.

44
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:45,340
So, you just sold out your sister

45
00:03:45,340 --> 00:03:47,100
right in front of our ancestor?

46
00:03:47,500 --> 00:03:48,700
I didn't.

47
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:50,060
Isn't he our ancestor?

48
00:03:50,060 --> 00:03:51,020
I knew our family

49
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:52,720
would definitely love Jianbing Guozi.

50
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:53,820
So, he had a bad impression

51
00:03:53,820 --> 00:03:55,220
of me from the start.

52
00:03:55,540 --> 00:03:57,900
Shen Gongcai, you've ruined everything.

53
00:03:57,900 --> 00:04:00,180
Jicai, instead of complaining about me,

54
00:04:00,420 --> 00:04:01,260
why don't you

55
00:04:01,740 --> 00:04:02,900
think of a way

56
00:04:02,900 --> 00:04:04,060
to get close to our ancestor

57
00:04:04,060 --> 00:04:05,380
and sneak into Yunshui Manor?

58
00:04:05,380 --> 00:04:06,420
I had a plan, okay?

59
00:04:07,740 --> 00:04:08,580
Well.

60
00:04:09,420 --> 00:04:10,260
Do you have money?

61
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:12,340
- I'll buy some other food.
- What?

62
00:04:12,340 --> 00:04:14,100
All you can do is eat, huh?

63
00:04:14,820 --> 00:04:16,860
Mom and Dad are working
in the inn's kitchen.

64
00:04:16,860 --> 00:04:17,800
Get up and go help them.

65
00:04:18,180 --> 00:04:20,060
Sure, I'll go in a bit.

66
00:04:20,380 --> 00:04:21,220
Now.

67
00:04:21,780 --> 00:04:23,500
I'll go at once.

68
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:24,340
I'll go.

69
00:04:24,980 --> 00:04:25,820
Get up!

70
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,820
Get up now!

71
00:04:26,820 --> 00:04:27,780
Get up!

72
00:04:27,780 --> 00:04:29,540
You ruined my plan, and you won't help?

73
00:04:29,540 --> 00:04:30,540
Shen Gongcai!

74
00:04:31,020 --> 00:04:32,380
Did I say I wouldn't go?

75
00:04:32,820 --> 00:04:33,660
Come on.

76
00:04:36,020 --> 00:04:37,220
(A rough start.)

77
00:04:37,380 --> 00:04:39,060
(Yunshui Manor)
(But our family has loved)

78
00:04:39,060 --> 00:04:40,580
(Jianbing Guozi for three generations.)

79
00:04:40,700 --> 00:04:41,780
(I just can't believe it.)

80
00:04:42,060 --> 00:04:43,920
(If I show up
before the ancestor every day,)

81
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:45,380
(he'll surely notice me.)

82
00:04:47,300 --> 00:04:48,140
Here.

83
00:04:49,460 --> 00:04:51,220
The latest flavor we've developed.

84
00:04:51,220 --> 00:04:52,260
Jianbing Guozi.

85
00:04:52,350 --> 00:04:53,940
Salty and sweet options are available.

86
00:04:53,940 --> 00:04:55,900
One qian each for Jianbing Guozi.

87
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,060
First blood.

88
00:05:01,180 --> 00:05:03,260
(Hold on,
the ancestor will come eventually.)

89
00:05:04,900 --> 00:05:05,740
Hold tight.

90
00:05:09,700 --> 00:05:12,500
The latest five-colored Jianbing Guozi.

91
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:14,380
Don't miss out as you pass by.

92
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:16,780
Strike while the iron is hot.

93
00:05:16,780 --> 00:05:18,580
Opportunities don't come every day.

94
00:05:18,700 --> 00:05:21,180
What a delicious five-colored pancake.

95
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:24,040
Five-colored pancake.

96
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,140
Double kill.

97
00:05:30,540 --> 00:05:31,620
Auntie, you're amazing.

98
00:05:32,700 --> 00:05:33,740
I'll take this pancake.

99
00:05:33,740 --> 00:05:34,740
- Tasty.
- Sure.

100
00:05:34,860 --> 00:05:36,120
- I'll take it.
- No pushing.

101
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,820
The curfew is approaching.
Hurry home now.

102
00:05:37,820 --> 00:05:39,300
Triple kill.

103
00:05:39,300 --> 00:05:40,240
We'll leave now.

104
00:05:47,260 --> 00:05:48,100
He's coming.

105
00:05:50,940 --> 00:05:52,220
Jianbing Guozi!

106
00:05:53,140 --> 00:05:55,820
Freshly baked Jianbing Guozi!

107
00:05:56,010 --> 00:05:56,980
Delicious and affordable!

108
00:05:56,980 --> 00:05:58,300
Young Master.

109
00:05:58,300 --> 00:05:59,180
It's not pricey.

110
00:05:59,180 --> 00:06:00,620
- I woke up late.
- Jianbing Guozi.

111
00:06:00,620 --> 00:06:01,680
Why didn't you wake me up?

112
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:04,000
- Delicious Jianbing Guozi.
- I'll prepare the carriage.

113
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,400
Delicious and affordable.

114
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,340
Defeat.

115
00:06:07,380 --> 00:06:08,540
Our ancestor

116
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:10,460
must be the person who dislikes

117
00:06:10,460 --> 00:06:12,660
Jianbing Guozi the most in the world.

118
00:06:14,180 --> 00:06:18,620
(Xuanzheng Gate)

119
00:06:18,860 --> 00:06:19,700
Vice Minister Zhang.

120
00:06:21,140 --> 00:06:22,300
Please wait.

121
00:06:24,300 --> 00:06:26,760
I am Pei Fei,
the newly appointed Censor.

122
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:29,520
(Pei Fei, Censor of the Censorate)
To create a register for Mr. Lin,

123
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,820
I need the document

124
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:33,220
from the Ministry of Personnel.

125
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:34,580
I wonder if you

126
00:06:34,780 --> 00:06:36,180
could do me a favor.

127
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:38,020
How could it not be given to you?

128
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:40,420
They're probably too busy.

129
00:06:40,780 --> 00:06:42,700
Censor Pei, please wait.

130
00:06:49,540 --> 00:06:50,380
Vice Minister Zhang.

131
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:53,060
I work for His Majesty.

132
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:55,020
I don't have time to deal
with a document.

133
00:06:55,340 --> 00:06:57,140
Censor Pei, if you keep pestering me...

134
00:06:57,860 --> 00:06:58,700
Vice Minister Zhang.

135
00:07:04,980 --> 00:07:06,260
Vice Prefect Lin.

136
00:07:07,180 --> 00:07:08,980
What do you need?

137
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:10,660
I've just taken office.

138
00:07:10,860 --> 00:07:12,500
Without a register at the Censorate,

139
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:13,700
it might affect the evaluation.

140
00:07:14,260 --> 00:07:15,660
If you're too busy,

141
00:07:15,820 --> 00:07:17,900
I can get the document myself

142
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:19,180
and deliver it to Censor Pei.

143
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:21,940
My subordinates are just too busy.

144
00:07:22,300 --> 00:07:24,940
How could I trouble you
with such a trifle?

145
00:07:25,140 --> 00:07:26,020
Tomorrow morning,

146
00:07:26,020 --> 00:07:28,500
I will send someone
to deliver the document

147
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:29,980
to the Censorate asap.

148
00:07:31,140 --> 00:07:31,980
Thank you.

149
00:07:36,740 --> 00:07:38,940
Thank you, Vice Prefect Lin.

150
00:07:39,980 --> 00:07:41,500
I've heard that you live far away.

151
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:43,980
Did you have breakfast before court?

152
00:07:47,860 --> 00:07:49,420
(Capital Prefecture)

153
00:07:49,420 --> 00:07:50,860
Every time I went to the Personnel,

154
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:53,300
(Capital Prefecture)
Mr. Zhang could always find an excuse.

155
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:55,660
And you asked me to share your carriage

156
00:07:55,940 --> 00:07:57,340
and have a meal at your residence.

157
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:58,700
If others see this,

158
00:07:59,140 --> 00:08:00,820
they will surely think we are close.

159
00:08:01,340 --> 00:08:03,140
If anyone wants
to make things hard for me,

160
00:08:03,220 --> 00:08:05,180
they will have to think twice.

161
00:08:05,900 --> 00:08:07,300
I really don't know

162
00:08:07,420 --> 00:08:09,140
how to repay your kindness.

163
00:08:09,380 --> 00:08:11,180
I'm also someone
in a foreign land alone.

164
00:08:11,540 --> 00:08:12,660
I can really empathize.

165
00:08:13,170 --> 00:08:14,940
Censor Pei, don't take it to heart.

166
00:08:15,700 --> 00:08:16,540
Young Master.

167
00:08:16,740 --> 00:08:17,580
Censor Pei.

168
00:08:29,660 --> 00:08:30,500
Thank you.

169
00:08:30,900 --> 00:08:31,740
Censor Pei,

170
00:08:31,860 --> 00:08:32,700
please.

171
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:37,780
You prefer light flavors?

172
00:08:38,020 --> 00:08:38,940
Not particularly.

173
00:08:39,380 --> 00:08:41,540
I just don't think it's necessary
to fuss over food.

174
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:43,040
Food is to fill my stomach.

175
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:44,380
If you're not used to it,

176
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,740
I can arrange something else.

177
00:08:45,740 --> 00:08:47,420
No, no, I'm used to it.

178
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:48,980
I grew up in the countryside.

179
00:08:49,380 --> 00:08:51,140
I'm very used to eating like this.

180
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:58,100
You helped me a lot today

181
00:08:58,340 --> 00:08:59,580
and even treated me to a meal.

182
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:01,340
I should return the favor.

183
00:09:01,700 --> 00:09:02,980
There's no need to be so polite.

184
00:09:02,980 --> 00:09:04,740
No, no, I must insist.

185
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:07,380
You can't possibly refuse a meal,
can you?

186
00:09:10,900 --> 00:09:13,580
(Yunshui Manor)

187
00:09:17,620 --> 00:09:18,460
Fortunately,

188
00:09:18,780 --> 00:09:20,300
Father bought Yunshui Manor

189
00:09:20,300 --> 00:09:21,580
under someone else's name.

190
00:09:22,220 --> 00:09:24,120
It wasn't listed
in the confiscation inventory,

191
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:26,300
so I could buy it back.

192
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:27,780
17 years ago,

193
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:29,840
when your father served as the Prefect,

194
00:09:30,100 --> 00:09:32,120
he was imprisoned
for selling official positions.

195
00:09:32,580 --> 00:09:35,220
The Censorate at that time
was all over him.

196
00:09:35,500 --> 00:09:36,680
The Cui family was slandered,

197
00:09:37,020 --> 00:09:38,700
and they had no small part in it.

198
00:09:39,220 --> 00:09:42,380
Why bother with Pei Fei?

199
00:09:43,220 --> 00:09:45,260
At that time, Censor Pei
was still at home mourning

200
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,820
and hadn't taken up his post here.

201
00:09:46,820 --> 00:09:47,660
What does this

202
00:09:48,660 --> 00:09:49,500
have to do with him?

203
00:09:51,580 --> 00:09:53,060
If we're talking about zodiac signs,

204
00:09:53,140 --> 00:09:54,660
you should be a vengeful one.

205
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:56,100
How could you not care?

206
00:09:57,340 --> 00:09:59,820
You think Pei Fei might be useful
when you need

207
00:09:59,820 --> 00:10:01,820
to investigate the Censorate, right?

208
00:10:19,300 --> 00:10:20,300
(Be cautious.)

209
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:33,260
My father used to keep all his books

210
00:10:33,260 --> 00:10:34,260
and notes in the study.

211
00:10:34,700 --> 00:10:36,300
Perhaps we can find some clues there.

212
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:39,220
Everyone outside
has been taken care of, right?

213
00:10:39,420 --> 00:10:40,380
Don't worry.

214
00:10:40,900 --> 00:10:42,260
Even a mouse

215
00:10:42,260 --> 00:10:43,500
wouldn't get in here.

216
00:10:52,820 --> 00:10:55,260
(Langhuan Chamber)

217
00:11:04,300 --> 00:11:06,140
Father built this hidden door secretly.

218
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:08,200
Yunshui Manor
has been abandoned for years,

219
00:11:08,220 --> 00:11:09,380
so no one has discovered it.

220
00:11:12,500 --> 00:11:14,460
What kind of lock is this?

221
00:11:14,700 --> 00:11:16,220
Your father made it.

222
00:11:16,660 --> 00:11:18,020
He found it years ago.

223
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:19,860
Seemingly from the Western Regions.

224
00:11:20,380 --> 00:11:22,180
Only my mother and he
knew how to open it.

225
00:11:22,540 --> 00:11:24,140
They never allowed me to play in here,

226
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:25,540
always keeping this place locked.

227
00:11:25,540 --> 00:11:26,860
So, you don't know

228
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:29,160
how to open it?

229
00:11:30,460 --> 00:11:31,440
It shouldn't be too hard.

230
00:11:37,660 --> 00:11:39,540
There's no keyhole.

231
00:11:50,540 --> 00:11:51,500
Very well.

232
00:11:51,820 --> 00:11:53,280
Interesting.

233
00:12:14,340 --> 00:12:16,340
(Congrats on getting a free tasting)

234
00:12:23,540 --> 00:12:25,220
Auntie, you're so amazing.

235
00:12:25,380 --> 00:12:27,120
How did you come up with this idea?

236
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,320
It's because of our ancestor.

237
00:12:28,340 --> 00:12:30,180
I don't believe

238
00:12:30,180 --> 00:12:32,340
he can resist the temptation
of a free meal.

239
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:35,620
(Jingsi Study)

240
00:12:36,620 --> 00:12:37,460
Young Master,

241
00:12:38,060 --> 00:12:41,100
are we really stuck

242
00:12:41,340 --> 00:12:42,460
by a Western Regions lock?

243
00:12:42,660 --> 00:12:43,900
Don't worry.

244
00:12:43,900 --> 00:12:45,120
We'll figure it out eventually.

245
00:12:58,700 --> 00:13:02,260
(Jingsi Study)

246
00:13:03,940 --> 00:13:04,780
What is this?

247
00:13:25,900 --> 00:13:30,540
(Congrats on getting a free tasting
at Shen's Diner)

248
00:13:34,460 --> 00:13:35,900
Didn't you say

249
00:13:36,540 --> 00:13:38,540
not even a mouse would get in here?

250
00:13:39,660 --> 00:13:40,940
I'll go find them right now.

251
00:13:41,140 --> 00:13:41,980
Come back.

252
00:13:48,900 --> 00:13:50,280
Shen's Diner?

253
00:13:50,940 --> 00:13:53,020
The ones who were selling pancakes

254
00:13:53,180 --> 00:13:54,100
are the Shens, right?

255
00:13:55,020 --> 00:13:56,020
That's right.

256
00:13:56,580 --> 00:13:57,660
If it really is them,

257
00:13:58,260 --> 00:14:00,300
the way they write, fold things,

258
00:14:00,740 --> 00:14:02,780
run their business, and they talk...

259
00:14:02,780 --> 00:14:03,920
Everything seems a bit odd.

260
00:14:05,100 --> 00:14:06,140
It's as if they're trying

261
00:14:06,540 --> 00:14:08,140
to get my attention.

262
00:14:09,940 --> 00:14:10,980
Could it be

263
00:14:12,370 --> 00:14:14,780
that someone has discovered your secret?

264
00:14:18,660 --> 00:14:22,860
(Minfu Inn)

265
00:14:26,860 --> 00:14:28,660
I've drawn for four hours.

266
00:14:29,460 --> 00:14:32,300
How could someone
not be interested in a free meal?

267
00:14:32,620 --> 00:14:35,380
Auntie, should we give up?

268
00:14:35,940 --> 00:14:37,260
Let's think of another way.

269
00:14:40,700 --> 00:14:43,180
My god, give me a miracle.

270
00:14:43,180 --> 00:14:44,380
Tell me how I can get in touch

271
00:14:44,380 --> 00:14:46,300
with our ancestor.

272
00:15:09,660 --> 00:15:11,740
How should I treat
the Vice Prefect to a meal?

273
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:13,980
This is all too expensive.

274
00:15:15,620 --> 00:15:17,620
My monthly salary won't cover it.

275
00:15:28,580 --> 00:15:30,660
(Congrats)
Anyone holding this flyer

276
00:15:30,940 --> 00:15:34,460
can enjoy a free tasting

277
00:15:35,660 --> 00:15:37,260
at Earth Room I, Minfu Inn.

278
00:15:44,420 --> 00:15:46,740
Censor Pei,
where are you taking me to eat?

279
00:15:47,980 --> 00:15:49,100
You're new here.

280
00:15:49,100 --> 00:15:51,180
You probably don't know much
about Yong'an.

281
00:15:51,540 --> 00:15:52,420
As the saying goes,

282
00:15:53,060 --> 00:15:55,000
