00:27:36,260 --> 00:27:37,660
Now, we're not only engaged

559
00:27:37,660 --> 00:27:38,900
but also have physical intimacy.

560
00:27:39,060 --> 00:27:40,500
You must take responsibility for me.

561
00:27:40,660 --> 00:27:42,420
If you don't let us stay
in Yunshui Manor,

562
00:27:42,540 --> 00:27:44,780
I'll go to the streets and cry
about your abandonment.

563
00:27:47,740 --> 00:27:48,580
I'll count to three.

564
00:27:49,260 --> 00:27:50,100
One.

565
00:27:50,780 --> 00:27:51,620
Two.

566
00:27:52,020 --> 00:27:52,860
Three.

567
00:27:55,360 --> 00:27:56,580
Everyone, please judge for me.

568
00:27:56,580 --> 00:27:57,580
Vice Prefect Lin, he...

569
00:27:57,820 --> 00:27:58,660
I agree.

570
00:28:02,020 --> 00:28:03,580
How virtuous of you.

571
00:28:03,580 --> 00:28:05,420
You won't stoop to my level.

572
00:28:05,460 --> 00:28:06,900
I'm truly grateful.

573
00:28:07,160 --> 00:28:08,980
You're a gentleman
who values your promises.

574
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:10,900
I believe you won't go back
on your word.

575
00:28:11,100 --> 00:28:12,020
I also promise you

576
00:28:12,020 --> 00:28:13,060
that I won't reveal

577
00:28:13,060 --> 00:28:14,540
anything I know to anyone else.

578
00:28:14,600 --> 00:28:15,500
Not a third person...

579
00:28:15,500 --> 00:28:17,140
Not an eighth person in this world

580
00:28:20,780 --> 00:28:22,300
will know about our relationship.

581
00:28:24,420 --> 00:28:25,720
(With important matters at hand,)

582
00:28:25,740 --> 00:28:27,160
(this family is really suspicious.)

583
00:28:27,620 --> 00:28:28,620
(I'll take them back)

584
00:28:29,340 --> 00:28:30,420
(and clear things up.)

585
00:28:32,020 --> 00:28:34,700
(Yunshui Manor)

586
00:28:34,700 --> 00:28:36,700
(Virtue and Fragrance)

587
00:28:36,700 --> 00:28:37,700
Yunshui Manor

588
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:39,140
is not quite the same

589
00:28:39,420 --> 00:28:40,500
as the modern one.

590
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:41,620
Yes, it's not the same.

591
00:28:41,620 --> 00:28:43,120
Can we really stay here for free?

592
00:28:43,120 --> 00:28:44,180
I'm afraid Vice Prefect Lin

593
00:28:44,180 --> 00:28:46,140
won't ask for money,
but he'll ask for our lives.

594
00:28:46,700 --> 00:28:48,420
Don't talk nonsense and scare Yangyang.

595
00:28:49,540 --> 00:28:50,780
Here he comes.

596
00:28:51,100 --> 00:28:51,940
Here he comes.

597
00:28:55,420 --> 00:28:56,380
Vice Prefect.

598
00:28:57,180 --> 00:28:58,020
Vice Prefect.

599
00:28:58,380 --> 00:29:00,540
If you stay in Yunshui Manor for now,

600
00:29:01,220 --> 00:29:02,420
others will surely gossip.

601
00:29:02,860 --> 00:29:04,740
Although we were engaged,

602
00:29:05,260 --> 00:29:07,060
we're not married after all.

603
00:29:07,740 --> 00:29:08,600
I really don't know

604
00:29:08,660 --> 00:29:10,940
what basis there is for us
to live under the same roof.

605
00:29:10,940 --> 00:29:13,260
Are you going back on your word?

606
00:29:13,540 --> 00:29:14,540
We've already moved

607
00:29:14,540 --> 00:29:16,100
all our luggage here.

608
00:29:16,100 --> 00:29:17,100
- You...
- No way.

609
00:29:17,100 --> 00:29:18,640
- Yes.
- I have to carry it all back?

610
00:29:20,820 --> 00:29:21,940
I'm just worried

611
00:29:22,340 --> 00:29:24,060
that if there's not even a proper basis,

612
00:29:24,620 --> 00:29:25,860
when my colleagues find out,

613
00:29:26,300 --> 00:29:27,980
they'll impeach me for a messy life.

614
00:29:28,780 --> 00:29:31,100
How should Lady Shen
and I explain ourselves?

615
00:29:31,580 --> 00:29:32,980
I read Dream of the Red Chamber...

616
00:29:34,860 --> 00:29:36,540
I read in a book

617
00:29:36,540 --> 00:29:37,780
that relatives can live together

618
00:29:37,780 --> 00:29:39,520
in an emergency,
even if they're unmarried.

619
00:29:39,560 --> 00:29:41,700
Besides, we have so many elders here.

620
00:29:41,700 --> 00:29:43,380
You can just tell people

621
00:29:43,500 --> 00:29:45,500
that I'm your cousin.

622
00:29:45,500 --> 00:29:47,700
We've fallen on hard times
and came for help.

623
00:29:47,700 --> 00:29:48,980
- Yes.
- Yes, yes.

624
00:29:48,980 --> 00:29:51,540
We're all relatives.

625
00:29:53,980 --> 00:29:54,820
Alright.

626
00:29:55,260 --> 00:29:56,420
It can hold off for a while.

627
00:29:57,220 --> 00:29:58,700
Thank you, Vice Prefect.

628
00:30:00,820 --> 00:30:01,900
(This guy)

629
00:30:02,060 --> 00:30:03,780
(clearly guided us to propose)

630
00:30:03,780 --> 00:30:05,060
(to live as relatives)

631
00:30:05,740 --> 00:30:08,580
(and made us feel
like we're troubling him.)

632
00:30:08,940 --> 00:30:10,340
(As expected of our ancestor.)

633
00:30:10,740 --> 00:30:12,100
(Also a cunning merchant.)

634
00:30:12,860 --> 00:30:14,900
You reluctantly took us in,

635
00:30:14,900 --> 00:30:16,500
and we're reasonable people.

636
00:30:16,740 --> 00:30:18,740
The youngest Vice Prefect in history

637
00:30:18,740 --> 00:30:20,020
can't have an unmarried wife

638
00:30:20,020 --> 00:30:21,420
from the countryside like me.

639
00:30:21,900 --> 00:30:23,580
Calling us cousins is the best solution.

640
00:30:23,740 --> 00:30:24,700
I understand the rules.

641
00:30:24,700 --> 00:30:27,000
The first step to success is
to cut ties with your lover.

642
00:30:28,500 --> 00:30:31,180
The first step to success is
to cut ties with your lover?

643
00:30:33,380 --> 00:30:35,180
It means I know you don't want

644
00:30:35,740 --> 00:30:36,580
to marry me.

645
00:30:39,340 --> 00:30:41,860
You're not like an ordinary young lady.

646
00:30:42,260 --> 00:30:43,100
You don't seem sad

647
00:30:43,380 --> 00:30:44,940
after losing your marriage.

648
00:30:46,980 --> 00:30:47,820
No.

649
00:30:48,540 --> 00:30:50,540
I'm just putting on a brave face.

650
00:30:51,580 --> 00:30:53,900
She's very sad.

651
00:30:53,900 --> 00:30:55,500
Yes, quite upset.

652
00:30:59,220 --> 00:31:00,540
The west wing is ready.

653
00:31:00,540 --> 00:31:01,380
Everyone,

654
00:31:01,580 --> 00:31:02,940
you can settle down here for now.

655
00:31:04,600 --> 00:31:05,540
Thank you, Vice Prefect.

656
00:31:05,540 --> 00:31:07,060
Thank you, thank you.

657
00:31:09,180 --> 00:31:10,020
Liu Chang.

658
00:31:10,260 --> 00:31:11,100
Everyone,

659
00:31:11,540 --> 00:31:12,420
please.

660
00:31:12,420 --> 00:31:13,580
Alright, alright.

661
00:31:14,420 --> 00:31:15,580
Let's go pick rooms.

662
00:31:15,580 --> 00:31:17,420
What about me? You're leaving?

663
00:31:17,820 --> 00:31:18,780
Auntie, hurry up.

664
00:31:19,980 --> 00:31:20,920
- Slow down.
- Hurry.

665
00:31:20,940 --> 00:31:22,260
At least help me carry something.

666
00:31:28,300 --> 00:31:30,460
(Start Near to Go Far)

667
00:31:37,500 --> 00:31:38,380
Lady Shen.

668
00:31:39,540 --> 00:31:40,420
Vice Prefect Lin.

669
00:31:41,060 --> 00:31:42,540
Ancestors,

670
00:31:43,060 --> 00:31:44,340
