671
00:31:44,980 --> 00:31:46,420
Please forgive us.

672
00:31:50,420 --> 00:31:52,660
Lady Shen, I had no other choice

673
00:31:52,660 --> 00:31:54,020
but this desperate measure.

674
00:31:54,140 --> 00:31:55,860
Who knew it'd actually work?

675
00:31:55,860 --> 00:31:56,820
Yes.

676
00:31:56,940 --> 00:31:58,060
If we hadn't said that,

677
00:31:58,060 --> 00:31:59,860
Vice Prefect Lin would've killed us.

678
00:31:59,860 --> 00:32:01,580
We were left with no other option.

679
00:32:02,900 --> 00:32:04,660
But it was mostly Jicai's idea.

680
00:32:04,660 --> 00:32:05,740
She's the mastermind.

681
00:32:06,300 --> 00:32:07,260
You brat.

682
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:10,180
Ancestors,

683
00:32:10,540 --> 00:32:12,260
we truly had no idea

684
00:32:12,260 --> 00:32:14,180
that Vice Prefect Lin had a fiancée

685
00:32:14,180 --> 00:32:15,540
before he married into our family.

686
00:32:15,980 --> 00:32:17,140
You two

687
00:32:17,540 --> 00:32:18,980
will have to sort it out

688
00:32:18,980 --> 00:32:20,980
down there in the afterlife.

689
00:32:22,840 --> 00:32:23,780
What's the matter now?

690
00:32:23,780 --> 00:32:25,140
Is this the point?

691
00:32:25,340 --> 00:32:27,100
You can't even repent properly.

692
00:32:29,540 --> 00:32:30,380
Ancestors,

693
00:32:30,980 --> 00:32:33,260
we will find a way back asap

694
00:32:33,380 --> 00:32:35,060
to end this absurdity.

695
00:32:35,540 --> 00:32:36,600
We've offended you greatly.

696
00:32:36,780 --> 00:32:37,700
Please forgive us.

697
00:32:37,900 --> 00:32:38,980
Forgive us.

698
00:32:38,980 --> 00:32:40,020
We're really sorry.

699
00:32:40,460 --> 00:32:42,900
Sorry, sorry.

700
00:32:43,100 --> 00:32:44,670
- Sorry, Ancestors.
- I'm sorry.

701
00:32:45,100 --> 00:32:45,940
I'm sorry.

702
00:32:46,900 --> 00:32:47,740
Jicai,

703
00:32:48,540 --> 00:32:50,180
do you think that such a big lie

704
00:32:50,180 --> 00:32:52,260
might cause a butterfly effect?

705
00:32:52,260 --> 00:32:53,700
Because we changed the past,

706
00:32:53,700 --> 00:32:55,100
it might affect the future?

707
00:32:55,740 --> 00:32:56,580
That would be bad.

708
00:32:56,780 --> 00:32:58,060
Then there wouldn't be us, right?

709
00:32:58,250 --> 00:32:59,100
Yes. Well...

710
00:32:59,100 --> 00:33:00,400
There's no other way.

711
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:02,420
If we hadn't said that,
there would be no future.

712
00:33:02,420 --> 00:33:03,860
We'd have been killed at once.

713
00:33:11,060 --> 00:33:12,380
Yangyang, come here.

714
00:33:13,060 --> 00:33:15,040
- What's that sound?
- Someone seems to be there.

715
00:33:15,140 --> 00:33:16,020
As expected.

716
00:33:16,740 --> 00:33:17,900
What do you mean?

717
00:33:21,580 --> 00:33:23,980
He's spying on us as expected.

718
00:33:28,020 --> 00:33:28,860
What do you mean?

719
00:33:30,220 --> 00:33:31,320
I only understood "black".

720
00:33:32,220 --> 00:33:33,060
It's he.

721
00:33:40,260 --> 00:33:43,940
(Permutations and combinations)

722
00:34:05,980 --> 00:34:06,820
Young Master.

723
00:34:09,540 --> 00:34:10,500
This family

724
00:34:10,820 --> 00:34:11,860
hasn't slept.

725
00:34:12,380 --> 00:34:14,380
They're huddled together, muttering.

726
00:34:14,580 --> 00:34:16,580
I can't quite make out
what they're saying.

727
00:34:17,060 --> 00:34:19,340
What do you plan to do next?

728
00:34:19,980 --> 00:34:21,940
They went through all this trouble
to get here.

729
00:34:22,460 --> 00:34:23,940
They won't just stay quietly.

730
00:34:24,180 --> 00:34:25,140
Wait for them to move.

731
00:34:28,340 --> 00:34:29,180
Liu Chang,

732
00:34:30,540 --> 00:34:32,940
my parents did arrange
a marriage for me,

733
00:34:33,380 --> 00:34:34,620
but as far as I can remember,

734
00:34:35,220 --> 00:34:36,580
she was a Zheng,

735
00:34:37,140 --> 00:34:38,060
not a Shen.

736
00:34:38,460 --> 00:34:39,440
Do you remember anything?

737
00:34:39,700 --> 00:34:41,860
I've been in the Cui family
since I was young,

738
00:34:42,220 --> 00:34:44,620
but I've always been doing odd jobs.

739
00:34:45,700 --> 00:34:47,220
I've never heard of these things.

740
00:34:52,140 --> 00:34:52,980
Look.

741
00:34:53,220 --> 00:34:55,100
I just taught him
how to make a Sinan chariot,

742
00:34:55,460 --> 00:34:57,340
and he's been busy with it all day.

743
00:35:03,500 --> 00:35:04,340
Father, Mother.

744
00:35:04,580 --> 00:35:06,060
Father, I've learned how to make this.

745
00:35:06,060 --> 00:35:06,900
Let me see.

746
00:35:09,540 --> 00:35:11,500
This is so exquisite.

747
00:35:11,900 --> 00:35:13,060
Good, good.

748
00:35:14,660 --> 00:35:15,900
The Sinan chariot can be used

749
00:35:16,540 --> 00:35:19,180
for transporting goods during war,

750
00:35:20,140 --> 00:35:22,820
but it doesn't mean
it's always a good thing.

751
00:35:23,500 --> 00:35:24,580
Our family

752
00:35:24,820 --> 00:35:26,420
should be good generals during wartime,

753
00:35:27,060 --> 00:35:28,060
protecting our country,

754
00:35:28,140 --> 00:35:29,820
- but we still hope...
- But we still hope

755
00:35:29,820 --> 00:35:33,100
that every day is as peaceful as today,

756
00:35:33,100 --> 00:35:35,300
and we only need to be loyal,

757
00:35:35,300 --> 00:35:37,280
- protecting the people.
- Protecting the people.

758
00:35:38,780 --> 00:35:40,020
Alright, I won't say more.

759
00:35:40,860 --> 00:35:41,900
Your mother will tell you.

760
00:35:44,660 --> 00:35:46,780
Che, actually,

761
00:35:46,780 --> 00:35:49,380
we have arranged
a marriage for you today.

762
00:35:49,780 --> 00:35:51,020
When you grow up,

763
00:35:51,020 --> 00:35:52,900
you must treat the young lady well.

764
00:35:52,900 --> 00:35:54,380
Why arrange a marriage?

765
00:35:54,940 --> 00:35:56,220
What's the use of a wife?

766
00:35:56,740 --> 00:35:58,860
She can't make a Sinan chariot for me.

767
00:35:59,260 --> 00:36:00,300
Che,

768
00:36:00,540 --> 00:36:02,740
because we

769
00:36:02,740 --> 00:36:04,300
can't be with you forever,

770
00:36:04,980 --> 00:36:07,740
so we hope you can have your own family.

771
00:36:08,340 --> 00:36:10,980
Don't you always want to be a great man?

772
00:36:11,660 --> 00:36:14,180
A great man should be like your father,

773
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:16,620
accountable to friends,
relatives, and family,

774
00:36:16,620 --> 00:36:18,580
and live up to the people and the world.

775
00:36:31,620 --> 00:36:32,500
Check thoroughly.

776
00:36:39,260 --> 00:36:40,360
Don't leave anyone behind.

777
00:36:40,460 --> 00:36:41,700
Mother.

778
00:36:42,500 --> 00:36:44,900
Young Master, calm down.

779
00:37:03,620 --> 00:37:05,380
My leg seems to be broken.

780
00:37:06,180 --> 00:37:07,380
I can't walk.

781
00:37:07,420 --> 00:37:08,260
Search carefully.

782
00:37:08,460 --> 00:37:09,940
Leave no one alive.

783
00:37:15,300 --> 00:37:16,300
Young Master,

784
00:37:16,540 --> 00:37:17,580
why don't you

785
00:37:17,980 --> 00:37:19,380
just leave me behind?

786
00:37:21,420 --> 00:37:23,300
I'm just a servant
in the outer courtyard.

787
00:37:23,820 --> 00:37:24,740
Your family

788
00:37:25,100 --> 00:37:26,700
has always treated me well.

789
00:37:27,260 --> 00:37:28,820
I can't let

790
00:37:29,900 --> 00:37:32,020
the last Cui die

791
00:37:33,060 --> 00:37:34,460
because of me.

792
00:37:34,470 --> 00:37:35,380
Shut up, Liu Chang.

793
00:37:35,380 --> 00:37:36,220
Look further inside.

794
00:37:38,300 --> 00:37:39,740
Do you want to draw everyone here?

795
00:37:40,380 --> 00:37:41,580
We're not at a dead end yet.

796
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:43,180
Let me carry you.

797
00:37:44,700 --> 00:37:45,540
Che,

798
00:37:45,940 --> 00:37:47,860
your father would never do such a thing.

799
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:49,660
You must survive,

800
00:37:50,100 --> 00:37:51,220
find out the truth,

801
00:37:51,540 --> 00:37:52,980
and clear our family's name.

802
00:37:58,380 --> 00:37:59,740
But so many years have passed.

803
00:37:59,980 --> 00:38:02,540
Your appearance has changed greatly.

804
00:38:03,340 --> 00:38:04,580
How did this family

805
00:38:04,580 --> 00:38:06,620
