806
00:38:08,500 --> 00:38:09,440
For the next few days,

807
00:38:09,540 --> 00:38:10,700
keep a close eye on them.

808
00:38:11,780 --> 00:38:12,980
I'll also find an opportunity

809
00:38:13,260 --> 00:38:14,660
to probe their background.

